signature: DeferredChanged<ChangedHeaders> diff(Map<String, Header>, Map<String, Header>, DiffContext)

enhanced_by.reason: Initialization of fields is necessary to ensure the OpenApiDiff instance is properly set up before performing header diffs.
Pre-processing the OpenAPI specifications can help in normalizing the data before performing the diff, ensuring more accurate results.
The method aggregates changes across different parts of the OpenAPI specification, including headers, which can be used to verify the overall diff results.
Both methods involve comparing headers and can provide similar output structures, making it easier to construct assertions for the diff method.
